{
  "stem": "24544.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told mother-- my mother, always-- I feel the burning smell like at the harvest of the-- of the vineyard.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we thought that this was a kitchen, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So Dante's hell was heaven to describe--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was taken to the gas chamber with the gypsies together because everyone over there beside the gypsies was between 14 and 16-years-old boys, mostly Hungarians, because this time it wasn't any more 14, 16 years old from Lithuania or Poland or anywhere.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was all of them, 14 and 16-years-old young boys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure, sure sorry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Sajopalfalva we went to live to Felsozsolca.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, because we became bigger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't have any Jewish life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was a dead end for us, the children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we went to the city anyway to schooling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we went to Felsozsolca.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was 119 Jewish people there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the young people came together Saturday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have the shul.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have also a shechot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But time to time, one of the rabbi, real rabbi, came about 10 kilometers to see us and to giving us the line, how can we go further?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And went to school, to Miskolc.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What kind of a home did you have there in Felsozsolca?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beautiful.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We built it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We built that with two big stores, butcher and the grocery stores.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's true, we didn't have a pipe for water.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we have a very small, little place, which we called bathroom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was only a so-called [NON-ENGLISH]--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wash basin, yes, and we took the water in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we have a bathroom we could sit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had one-- my own room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was a big things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The house was beautiful and was continuing with-- for the guy with family who take care of our farm.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
